                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. shown traces of intensive use; many fols.
                           are stained with wax and dirt. Some fols. are affected by humidity. The
                           Ms. has been resewn. The leather cover has been cut off at the spine,
                           probably to facilitate resewing. Tears on the cover have been amended.
                           The endleaves are partly detached from the rest of the Ms. f. 1 is of
                           smaller size. Many fols. have been damaged by rodents, sometimes with
                           text loss, e.g., <locus target="#51">51</locus>, 52, 53, 54, 55, 56.&#xD;
                           Holes or tears amended on <locus target="#82">82</locus>, 94, 102,
